Internship Offer 
 
Dear Harikrishnan C J, 
 17th Sep 2025 
Email: harikrishnancj5@gmail.com 
Ph.: 7025200884 
 
 
We are pleased to extend congratulations on your successful selection for the role of AI Internship 
with Saasvaap Techies Pvt. Ltd. We are excited to welcome you to our team, and your internship 
is scheduled for 6 Months and the start date commence on September 22nd 2025. 
Please find below the terms and conditions of your internship with our company: 
 
 
Your project assignments and responsibilities will be determined by the assigned Lead, in 
accordance with the outlined terms and conditions. 
 
No monetary compensation or employee benefits are provided during the internship period. 
 
The internship mandates your presence at our Cochin Office from Monday to Friday, 9:00 
am to 6:00 pm 
 
Prior to commencing your internship, you will be required to sign a confidentiality agreement 
with the company. 
 
An extensive assessment will be conducted at the conclusion of the internship, and the 
company reserves the right to extend the duration based on evaluated skills and 
performance. 
Kindly acknowledge your acceptance of these terms within 48 hours of receiving this letter. 
Failure to do so may lead to the cancellation of the internship offer. 
We are enthusiastic about the opportunity to have you join our organization and believe that your 
skills and dedication will greatly contribute to our team's success. 
Warm regards, 
Simitha.V.S 
Manager (HR & Admin.) 
Saasvaap Techies Pvt. Ltd.
